 herb mixture in mixing bowl."},{"content":"Add another ⅓ reserved squid and prawns then cook <b>1-2 min\/Varoma\/\/speed <b>, until cooked to your preference. Carefully remove cooked squid and prawns then transfer to bowl with previous batch. Leave oil and herb mixture in mixing bowl."},{"content":"Add remaining ⅓ reserved squid and prawns then cook <b>1-2 min\/Varoma\/\/speed <b>, until cooked to your preference. Carefully remove cooked squid and prawns then transfer to bowl with reserved seafood. Transfer oil and herb mixture into a serving jug."},{"content":"Squeeze 1-2 lemon wedges over seafood. Garnish with remaining wedges and extra chopped parsley and coriander. Serve immediately."}],"hintsAndTricks":["This recipe is best when served immediately, so we recommend pre-preparing all of your ingredients, including garnishes, before you commence cooking your seafood in steps 4-7."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","20m","8 portions"]}